OCC: Just so there are no objections by Dachande Proto piccked up the fight 
on his own personal scanners.

 Proto arived at the battle. He particaly noticed a bot useing energy. He 
molded into the shape of the bot. He looked at the body. He wasnt fond of it. 
He looked at the other. A dragon. He transformed inot it. he thought... "Why 
would he stay in beast mode in a battle. He seems to be doing farely well 
just staying in it. Maybe he is stuck. Or maybe he doesnt want to show is 
true self just yet. What ever the reason. He watched with entertainment as 
the bots went at eachother. The dragon then formed a new type of armor. He 
tried to scan it but it was blocked. He wondered what it could do. He 
transformed into a liquid and watched.
